article_metadata.keywords: health insurance, anthem, cigna, obamacare, affordable care act, earnings, health care,
article_metadata.description: Health insurer Anthem, which is in the process of buying smaller rival Cigna, said on Wednesday its individual Obamacare exchange health plans weighed on fourth-quarter profit, causing it to miss analysts' expectations.
